snippet.title: The Sims 3 Diesel Stuff Official Trailer
snippet.description: It's time for successful living with The Sims 3 Diesel Stuff! Dress to impress! The Sims 3 Diesel Stuff contains the hottest fashions and home furnishings for your Sims from one of the world's most popular fashion brands. Style your Sims with the latest looks, straight from the Diesel runway. . Learn more about The Sims 3 Diesel Stuff here: http://thesims.com/en_US/the-sims-3-diesel-stuff Learn more about Diesel here: https://www.facebook.com/Diesel
